#!
# premade query answers

$ORIGIN example.com.
$TTL 3600

# reply IXFR request
ENTRY_BEGIN
MATCH opcode qtype qname serial=3
REPLY QUERY NOERROR
ADJUST copy_id
SECTION QUESTION
@ IN IXFR
SECTION ANSWER
# AXFR response for IXFR query.
@ 345600 IN SOA ns0.example.org. root 4 3600 28800 2419200 3600
@ 3600 NS ns.example.com.
ns 3600 IN A 10.0.0.1
a 3600 IN A 10.0.0.1
@ 345600 IN SOA ns0.example.org. root 4 3600 28800 2419200 3600
ENTRY_END
